name: 配信者
trans: Oh wow. Did you feel paralyzed?

name: 女性
text:
はい……私の場合は、ですけど……
で、そのまま体が宙に浮いて
trans:
Yes... I did, but...
I felt like my body was just floating in space.

name: 女性
text:
見下ろしてるんですよ、自分を
でも、すぐには自分だってわからなくて……
trans:
Looking down, I saw myself.
But I wasn't sure it was me right away...

name: 女性
text:
誰だろうって……
自分なのに自分じゃない、みたいな──
trans:
I wondered who that was...
It was as if that was me, but not me─

name: 配信者
text:
は～……すげ～
そんな感じなんすね～
trans:
Huh~... That's cool~
So that's what it felt like~

name: 配信者
text:
でもぶっちゃけ、幽体離脱って
体の錯覚とか言われてるじゃないですか～
trans:
But to be honest, they say that out-of-body
experiences are sometimes just a sensory illusion
of the body, right~

name: 女性
text:
あー、はい……
まぁ、私もあれがただの錯覚だって言われたら──
trans:
Ahh, yeah...
But if you told me that it was just an illusion─

name: 女性
text: もしかしたら、夢だったのかもしれないし……
trans: Perhaps it was just a dream...

name: 小糸
text:
と、透ちゃん……
もう、やめようよ……

name: 雛菜
text:
あ～！
透先輩、またやってる～！

name: 雛菜
trans: Did it work? The out-of-body experience thingy.

name: off
text:
体　が
宙に浮く

name: off
text:
自分なのに
自分　じゃない
trans:
That was me
but　not me

name: 雛菜
trans: Yum~, it's so cold and tasty~~~!

name: 小糸
text: か、買って正解だったね、ソフトクリーム……！
trans: T-This soft cream was the right buy, huh...!

name: 小糸
text:
じ、時間……？
え、えっと……今、５時半だよ

name: 雛菜
text:
透先輩～、早く食べないと
ソフトクリーム溶けちゃうよ～？
trans:
Toru-senpai, the soft cream will melt if you don't
gobble it up quick you know~?

name: 透
text:
やべー
ほんとに溶けてる
trans:
Oh noー
It's really melting all over.

name: 雛菜
text: だから早く食べないとって言ったのに～！
trans: I did tell you to eat it quickly, didn't I~!

name: 透
trans:
Eh...
I can taste it, though...

name: 円香
trans: ...What are you on about, since just now?

name: 小糸
text:
と、透ちゃん、大丈夫……？
具合、悪い？
trans:
I-Is something the matter, Toru-chan...?
Are you feeling alright?

name: 透
text:
……ふふっ
小糸ちゃんも、小糸ちゃんだ

name: 透
trans: It's all good. It's a dream afterall.

name: 雛菜
text: このアイスおいしそう～～～！

name: 小糸
text: うん、お店もオシャレだね……！
trans: Yea, and the store was so classy too...!

name: 円香
text:
でもこの人、さっきから喋ってばっかで
全然食べてない
trans:
But this person over here's been talking the
whole time and haven't even taken a bite.

name: 雛菜
text:
あ～！
アイス、溶けちゃいそう～！
trans:
Ah~!
The ice cream's gonna melt~!

name: 透
text:
ふふっ
大丈夫、夢だから
trans:
Hehe.
It's all good. It's a dream afterall.
